but can't change the way they are.

486
00:42:01,047 --> 00:42:02,890
People's ideals,

487
00:42:03,047 --> 00:42:04,856
the things one loves,

488
00:42:05,007 --> 00:42:06,816
the places we want to reach,

489
00:42:07,167 --> 00:42:08,851
