who won and who lost,

497
00:42:36,127 --> 00:42:38,573
and they point at us
like we're the plague.

498
00:42:38,727 --> 00:42:42,368
Feel no shame! Hold your head high,
we never hurt anyone.

499
00:42:42,527 --> 00:42:45,292
